<TITLE> Lay down arms: Tuku </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Meherpur, Dec 13 (bdnews24.com)  State minister for home Shamsul Haq Tuku on Sunday urged extremists in the troubled southwest to surrender and lay down arms. He called upon them to "emerge from the darkness" and "join in nation building activities and the preservation of democracy". Tuku was attending a views exchange meeting with Meherpur district law enforcers. bdn
